sequenceDiagram
    participant BackgroundService
    participant FinancialAPI
    participant PostgreSQL

    BackgroundService->>FinancialAPI: Check due recurrences
    FinancialAPI->>PostgreSQL: Query due RecurrenceSchedules
    PostgreSQL-->>FinancialAPI: Due schedules
    loop For each schedule
        FinancialAPI->>PostgreSQL: Create Transaction
        PostgreSQL-->>FinancialAPI: Transaction created
    end
    FinancialAPI-->>BackgroundService: 10 transactions generated